snippet.title: E3 2012: Star Wars: The Old Republic Sizzle Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out an E3 2012 sizzle trailer for Star Wars: The Old Republic, giving the viewers a sneak preview of what to expect in future updates.

Subscribe to GameSpot's E3 Show for full coverage:
